title: Growing Pains In Arizona
itunes:title: Growing Pains In Arizona
description:
Colin gives his reason why he doesn’t like the Arizona Cardinals so far, why Colts fans should be worried about Andrew Luck, why Tom Brady is a great leader, and why James Harden is a better scorer than Michael Jordan. Guests include Urban Meyer, Tom Telesco, Eric Mangini, Peter King, and Jason McIntyre.
